title: Speech perception experiment. Earn $1.50 for 15 minutes.
description: Listen to audio clips and type what you hear. Please only participate if you are a native speaker of English, and at most speak a few words of another language.
Answer.comments: I really liked this task, it was hard to understand some of what he was saying. Mostly in the beginning I had a hard time understanding what every word was. This has taken me 30 minutes to complete excluding the questions after the transcribing, I am hoping there is some bonus included. I am not sure how someone that is and only speaks english would be able to complete this with 100% focus in 15 minutes or less. If they are, I feel that the data you get from those workers will be junk. I do type fast, I took the study very seriously as I do with all my work. I think for those who really put the effort in to provide good honest data should be paid more.
Answer.guess_accent: India or somewhere located in the middle east.
Answer.language_background_free: I am a native American English speaker. I have lived in America my entire life and have never learned another language or have been outside of the United States of America.
